.opencode/skills/cli-claude-code/SKILL.md:258:| **Haiku** | `claude-haiku-4-5-20251001` | Fast, lightweight tasks (classification, formatting, simple queries) |
.opencode/skills/cli-claude-code/SKILL.md:260:**Selection guidance**: Default to Sonnet unless the task specifically needs deep reasoning (Opus + `--effort high`) or is trivially simple (Haiku for batch ops where speed > depth).
